metadata.name: Do you wanna taste something?
metadata.description:
“Like dreams, the senses have the ability to reveal things buried in the subconscious.  but this happens while we are awake…” 

tasting past experiences, scents, and desires….  
it's all about tasting but awake...


Tasting Past experiences on awake 

she  has never been able to carry the eggs they gave her well… She is one of those who go on the road with broken eggs.. 
All the sensitive things that don't fit in the her hand..


The work is made with oil paint, texture techniques on canvas.  
Physical Canvas Size: 50x50x2 cm

Orginal physical painting will be sent to the primary collector 

(This is not a print) .And the collector will receive it as a gift in a black satin sheath.
